body:
That string is a binary-encoded protocol buffer. If you want to render something more human readable, you'll need to parse it as a `tf.summary.Summary` object:

```python
summary_train = sess.run(write_op, feed_dict=feed_dict_train)

summary_pb = tf.summary.Summary()
summary_pb.ParseFromString(summary_train)
print(summary_pb)
```
